  "contentHtml": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:39px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">各学院：</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:43px;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:39px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">根据</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">《福建中医药大学学年学分制学籍管理实施细则（修订稿）》（校办〔</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">2019〕26号）</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">，经转出学院、转入学院审核，教务处专题会议审议，</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">同意</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">姚少锋</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">退役学生的转专业申请。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:43px;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:39px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">现将审批情况予以公示，公示期：</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">-</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">日。公示期间如有异议，请与教务处联系，联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">22861010，联系人：吴老师。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:39px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:39px;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">附件：</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">姚少锋</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">退役学